You need to get the kane-key-pair-oregon.pem from Jim

ssh -i kane-key-pair-oregon.pem ec2-user@[host name]


Install puppet and git:

sudo yum install puppet
sudo yum install git

Download the jimmutable library using git:

https://github.com/jim-kane/jimmutable.git

later, when you need to update, the command is: git pull origin master